  <refnamediv>
    <refname>RPI_softToneWrite</refname>
    <refpurpose>Function to update tone frquency on the soft tone pin</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   RPI_softToneWrite(pin,freq)
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>pin :</term>
      <listitem><para> soft tone pin</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>freq:</term>
      <listitem><para> frequency value to write</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
This function updates the tone frequency value on the given pin. The tone will be played until you set the frequency to 0.
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Examples</title>
   <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
RPI_softToneWrite(1,200)
   ]]></programlisting>
</refsection>

